adding support for large, multi-dimensional arrays and matrices, along with a large collection of high-level mathematical functions to operate on these arrays.\",\"Text\":\"NumPy - NumPy is a library for the Python programming language, adding support for large, multi-dimensional arrays and matrices, along with a large collection of high-level mathematical functions to operate on these arrays.\"},{\"FirstURL\":\"https://duckduckgo.com/SciPy\",\"Icon\":{\"Height\":\"\",\"URL\":\"\",\"Width\":\"\"},\"Result\":\"<a href=\\\"https://duckduckgo.com/SciPy\\\">SciPy</a> - SciPy is a free and open-source Python library used for scientific computing and technical computing.\",\"Text\":\"SciPy - SciPy is a free and open-source Python library used for scientific computing and technical computing.\"},{\"FirstURL\":\"https://duckduckgo.com/Project_Jupyter\",\"Icon\":{\"Height\":\"\",\"URL\":\"\",\"Width\":\"\"},\"Result\":\"<a href=\\\"https://duckduckgo.com/Project_Jupyter\\\">Jupyter</a> - Project Jupyter is a project to develop open-source software, open standards, and services for interactive computing across multiple programming languages.\",\"Text\":\"Jupyter - Project Jupyter is a project to develop open-source software, open standards, and services for interactive computing across multiple programming languages.\"},{\"FirstURL\":\"https://duckduckgo.com/PyTorch\",\"Icon\":{\"Height\":\"\",\"URL\":\"\",\"Width\":\"\"},\"Result\":\"<a href=\\\"https://duckduckgo.com/PyTorch\\\">PyTorch</a> - PyTorch is an open-source deep learning library, originally developed by Meta Platforms and currently developed with support from the Linux Foundation.\",\"Text\":\"PyTorch - PyTorch is an open-source deep learning library, originally developed by Meta Platforms and currently developed with support from the Linux Foundation.\"},{\"FirstURL\":\"https://duckduckgo.com/Cython\",\"Icon\":{\"Height\":\"\",\"URL\":\"\",\"Width\":\"\"},\"Result\":\"<a href=\\\"https://duckduckgo.com/Cython\\\">Cython</a> - Cython is a superset of the programming language Python, which allows developers to write Python code that yields performance comparable to that of C. Cython is a compiled language that is typically used to generate CPython extension modules.\",\"Text\":\"Cython - Cython is a superset of the programming language Python, which allows developers to write Python code that yields performance comparable to that of C. Cython is a compiled language that is typically used to generate CPython extension modules.\"},{\"FirstURL\":\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Pattern_matching_programming_languages\",\"Icon\":{\"Height\":\"\",\"URL\":\"\",\"Width\":\"\"},\"Result\":\"<a href=\\\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Pattern_matching_programming_languages\\\">Pattern matching programming languages</a>\",\"Text\":\"Pattern matching programming languages\"},{\"FirstURL\":\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Class-based_programming_languages\",\"Icon\":{\"Height\":\"\",\"URL\":\"\",\"Width\":\"\"},\"Result\":\"<a href=\\\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Class-based_programming_languages\\\">Class-based programming languages</a>\",\"Text\":\"Class-based programming languages\"},{\"FirstURL\":\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Multi-paradigm_programming_languages\",\"Icon\":{\"Height\":\"\",\"URL\":\"\",\"Width\":\"\"},\"Result\":\"<a href=\\\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Multi-paradigm_programming_languages\\\">Multi-paradigm programming languages</a>\",\"Text\":\"Multi-paradigm programming languages\"},{\"FirstURL\":\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Text-oriented_programming_languages\",\"Icon\":{\"Height\":\"\",\"URL\":\"\",\"Width\":\"\"},\"Result\":\"<a href=\\\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Text-oriented_programming_languages\\\">Text-oriented programming languages</a>\",\"Text\":\"Text-oriented programming languages\"},{\"FirstURL\":\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Concurrent_programming_languages\",\"Icon\":{\"Height\":\"\",\"URL\":\"\",\"Width\":\"\"},\"Result\":\"<a href=\\\"https://duckduckgo.com/c/Concurrent_programmin